51
00:04:46,710 --> 00:04:48,517
Drink some sweet ShuiRong 100.

52
00:04:48,893 --> 00:04:51,595
Take vitamins from five and a half lemons
to get enough supplements.

53
00:04:52,874 --> 00:04:54,746
