60
00:05:10,911 --> 00:05:15,134
Shu. I guarantee you in just a few years
you will definitely be a big star.

61
00:05:15,214 --> 00:05:17,816
By that time, I, Cheng Erluo,
will be your number one fan.

62
00:05:18,951 --> 00:05:20,721
