I, bodyguard Cheng, is back in action.

67
00:05:30,579 --> 00:05:31,698
How was it?

68
00:05:31,778 --> 00:05:34,041
Has anyone harassed you recently?

69
00:05:36,181 --> 00:05:37,277
No.

70
00:05:38,002 --> 00:05:40,591
