That's great.
Let them see our reconciliation.

74
00:05:48,901 --> 00:05:50,834
You wait for me. I'll go get changed.

75
00:05:50,914 --> 00:05:53,654
Sure. No worries, take your time.

76
00:05:53,734 --> 00:05:54,747
What to do?

77
00:05:54,827 --> 00:05:55,893
What's wrong with Xia Rui?

78
00:05:55,973 --> 00:05:57,072
Is she unhappy?

79
00:05:57,152 --> 00:05:59,829
