81
00:06:03,442 --> 00:06:05,886
Xia Rui, who bullied you?

82
00:06:07,010 --> 00:06:08,637
Si Bo, you're also here?

83
00:06:09,436 --> 00:06:11,912
I've always heard that
Yami cafe is pretty good.

84
00:06:11,992 --> 00:06:14,126
I'm free today anyway. So I came over.

85
00:06:14,948 --> 00:06:17,978
By the way, I suddenly remembered
I have something to deal with.

86
00:06:18,058 --> 00:06:19,198
I have to leave.

87
00:06:20,803 --> 00:06:22,395
Don't, Si Bo.

88
00:06:22,475 --> 00:06:24,069
You've just arrived
and you're leaving already?

89
00:06:24,149 --> 00:06:27,002
I've watched the competition video
against the sport college today.

90
00:06:27,082 --> 00:06:28,657
I have a question
I've been wanting to ask.

91
00:06:28,737 --> 00:06:30,409
If it's okay with you,

92
00:06:30,489 --> 00:06:31,654
can I have ten minutes?

93
00:06:31,734 --> 00:06:32,801
Sure.

94
00:06:33,993 --> 00:06:35,618
Xia Rui. Give us two cups.

95
00:06:35,698 --> 00:06:37,470
Give us two of the best.

96
00:06:38,284 --> 00:06:40,040
Quick, let me show you.

97
00:06:40,393 --> 00:06:41,560
Have you reconciled?

98
00:06:42,960 --> 00:06:44,977
It can't keep going on like this.

99
00:06:45,390 --> 00:06:46,842
That's right.

100
00:06:46,922 --> 00:06:50,056
Reasoning with a fool like him,
there is no point.

101
00:06:52,241 --> 00:06:54,481
Si Bo didn't look for you anymore
after that?

102
00:06:54,561 --> 00:06:56,628
Are you guys meeting
for the first time here?

103
00:06:57,248 --> 00:06:58,443
The first time.

104
00:06:58,931 --> 00:07:01,126
Then he's quite a gentleman.

105
00:07:01,206 --> 00:07:02,465
He kept his words.

106
00:07:03,114 --> 00:07:04,156
But...

107
00:07:04,498 --> 00:07:07,286
Why does it feel like
he's retreating in order to advance?

108
00:07:08,161 --> 00:07:10,509
It feels a bit weird.

109
00:07:11,586 --> 00:07:13,779
It's okay.
You have made it clear to him anyway.

110
00:07:13,859 --> 00:07:15,934
But this Cheng Erluo.

111
00:07:16,014 --> 00:07:19,594
It's a three people movie
but he's acting as if he's not in it.

112
00:07:20,155 --> 00:07:23,000
I think you need to make it clear to him.

113
00:07:23,361 --> 00:07:25,577
You see, even our Nan Xi has spoken.

114
00:07:27,281 --> 00:07:28,526
Say what?

115
00:07:28,841 --> 00:07:31,181
About Si Bo having a crush on me?

116
00:07:33,129 --> 00:07:34,050
No.

117
00:07:34,131 --> 00:07:37,250
It's telling Cheng Erluo
that you like him.

118
00:07:39,477 --> 00:07:40,573
Human feelings...

119
00:07:41,048 --> 00:07:43,404
are like these three glasses
of Shu iRong 100.

120
00:07:44,044 --> 00:07:46,399
Grapefruit stands for bitterness.

121
00:07:47,644 --> 00:07:51,486
Green lime stands for sweet and sour,
just like you.

122
00:07:52,303 --> 00:07:55,973
Then, lemon means youth without regrets.

123
00:07:56,054 --> 00:07:59,247
Like you, who's like a flower, fragrant.

124
00:07:59,919 --> 00:08:01,536
Both of you came a long way.

125
00:08:01,616 --> 00:08:03,612
And tasted everything along the way.

126
00:08:03,692 --> 00:08:05,091
You have to understand.

127
00:08:05,688 --> 00:08:07,768
He also has to understand.

128
00:08:10,383 --> 00:08:12,086
How do I tell him?

129
00:08:12,166 --> 00:08:14,174
Tell him that I'm sorry.

130
00:08:14,254 --> 00:08:17,296
You've only treated me like a sister.
But I've always liked you?

131
00:08:17,376 --> 00:08:19,593
Forget it, just go with the flow.

132
00:08:19,673 --> 00:08:22,550
No, you can't let this go with the flow.
You can't let it flow.

133
00:08:22,630 --> 00:08:24,762
Especially
when there's a third party involved.

134
00:08:24,842 --> 00:08:27,327
Like a suitor who's courting you.
That's even worse.

135
00:08:27,407 --> 00:08:28,719
Just look at that Cheng Erluo.

136
00:08:28,799 --> 00:08:30,494
Such an insensitive person.

137
00:08:30,574 --> 00:08:33,547
If you don't tell him,
he will never know you like him.

138
00:08:33,627 --> 00:08:35,941
So awkward,
why don't you resolve this mess at once.

139
00:08:36,021 --> 00:08:37,229
Isn't it right, Nan Xi?

140
00:08:38,328 --> 00:08:39,726
-Yes.
-See.

141
00:08:39,806 --> 00:08:42,548
Even Nan Xi
has become a relationship expert.

142
00:08:44,280 --> 00:08:47,417
Why can both you show affection
just by talking about my problem?

143
00:08:51,780 --> 00:08:55,447
You can invite him
to the Best Restaurant.

144
00:08:55,527 --> 00:08:56,713
Best Restaurant?

145
00:08:57,847 --> 00:08:59,156
You never heard of it?

146
00:09:00,651 --> 00:09:02,495
I heard it from my customers here.

147
00:09:02,575 --> 00:09:05,456
No unsuccessful confession
has ever happened in this Best Restaurant.

148
00:09:05,536 --> 00:09:07,949
If it doesn't succeed,
you just add a dessert.

149
00:09:08,029 --> 00:09:09,017
It'll surely work.

150
00:09:09,097 --> 00:09:11,389
Just give it a try,
that's a holy land for confession.

151
00:09:12,539 --> 00:09:16,450
Why are the three of you
whispering sneakily like mice?

152
00:09:16,530 --> 00:09:17,820
Are you talking behind my back?

153
00:09:17,900 --> 00:09:18,979
-Yes.
-No.

154
00:09:20,080 --> 00:09:21,181
Is it a yes or no?

155
00:09:21,261 --> 00:09:22,588
-No.
-Yes.

156
00:09:22,668 --> 00:09:25,017
Do we need to talk about you
behind your back?

157
00:09:25,097 --> 00:09:26,180
That's true.

158
00:09:27,026 --> 00:09:29,546
But it's really great
I got to bump into Si Bo today.

159
00:09:30,011 --> 00:09:32,621
You quite like this Si Bo, don't you?

160
00:09:32,701 --> 00:09:34,658
Of course! Let me tell you.

161
00:09:34,738 --> 00:09:39,375
Si Bo is the second most excellent person
I've met in my life.

162
00:09:39,455 --> 00:09:42,021
Of course, the most excellent is Nan Xi.

163
00:09:44,806 --> 00:09:46,574
I'm just telling the truth.

164
00:09:47,013 --> 00:09:48,897
But Si Bo is really nice.

165
00:09:48,977 --> 00:09:50,871
He even offered to help me
with practice next week.

166
00:09:50,951 --> 00:09:51,999
Shu.

167
00:09:52,501 --> 00:09:55,750
Do you particularly dislike Si Bo?

168
00:09:55,830 --> 00:09:59,105
