are avoiding each other today.

169
00:09:59,979 --> 00:10:03,420
At least you noticed that.

170
00:10:03,500 --> 00:10:05,336
Nothing, don't think about it.

171
00:10:05,416 --> 00:10:06,563
That's good then.

172
00:10:13,534 --> 00:10:15,376
I was thinking about taking a week off.

173
00:10:15,457 --> 00:10:18,067
But our coach is back,
he's asking me to come back.

174
00:10:18,147 --> 00:10:19,772
I guess I can't have dinner tonight.

175
00:10:19,852 --> 00:10:20,904
I'm leaving.

176
00:10:23,583 --> 00:10:27,556
Really, there's something
really wrong with his brain.

177
00:10:28,071 --> 00:10:32,276
