178
00:10:33,276 --> 00:10:35,373
It's okay, no need for that.

179
00:10:35,453 --> 00:10:37,506
It's almost end of semester.
Everyone's quite busy.

180
00:10:38,248 --> 00:10:40,498
You're just going to drag it like this?

181
00:10:42,138 --> 00:10:44,452
