I'll wait for your good news.

183
00:10:57,784 --> 00:10:59,748
Great, great, great.

184
00:11:06,501 --> 00:11:07,711
Nan Xi.

185
00:11:08,259 --> 00:11:09,387
Come quickly!

186
00:11:09,467 --> 00:11:10,494
Okay.

187
