Gently, gently.

191
00:11:27,769 --> 00:11:30,084
Long live, mom.

192
00:11:30,164 --> 00:11:31,410
My goodness.

193
00:11:34,670 --> 00:11:36,368
Coffee machine?

194
00:11:40,586 --> 00:11:41,991
Don't worry.

195
00:11:42,071 --> 00:11:44,021
I won't treat you like a guinea pig.

196
