216
00:12:46,829 --> 00:12:48,872
I came up with a new formula.

217
00:12:49,177 --> 00:12:50,404
I have to try.

218
00:12:56,330 --> 00:12:59,166
Xia Rui, I have to concentrate
on one thing at a time.

219
00:12:59,246 --> 00:13:00,370
I can't multi-task.

220
00:13:00,450 --> 00:13:01,666
I'll wash the cup first.

221
00:13:01,984 --> 00:13:05,607
You can taste my coffee
while washing the cups.

222
00:13:08,544 --> 00:13:09,584
