224
00:13:16,042 --> 00:13:17,531
True, a bit bitter.

225
00:13:18,135 --> 00:13:19,728
Must've used the wrong beans,
let me try again.

226
00:13:19,808 --> 00:13:22,971
Xia Rui, I think
it's because I've drank too much.

227
00:13:23,051 --> 00:13:25,214
I can't taste it anymore.

228
00:13:26,316 --> 00:13:28,175
Then, take a rest and try again later.

229
00:13:34,194 --> 00:13:36,061
