00:14:14,257 --> 00:14:15,253
Sleep like this.

236
00:14:48,728 --> 00:14:50,031
You first.

237
00:14:52,046 --> 00:14:53,367
You go first.

238
00:14:54,325 --> 00:14:55,360
It's fine.

239
00:14:55,440 --> 00:14:57,592
I'm not in a hurry.

240
00:14:58,544 --> 00:15:01,196
I'm also not in a hurry.

241
00:15:02,543 --> 00:15:03,590
Well.

242
00:15:04,105 --> 00:15:06,735
