244
00:15:10,044 --> 00:15:11,500
Is that so?

245
00:15:11,580 --> 00:15:12,607
Yes.

246
00:15:12,687 --> 00:15:15,291
I'll go first then.

247
00:15:15,371 --> 00:15:17,778
Sure, you go first.

248
00:15:17,858 --> 00:15:19,170
Really?

249
00:15:19,872 --> 00:15:21,006
Go!

250
00:15:21,547 --> 00:15:22,444
