251
00:15:39,893 --> 00:15:40,968
Not too bad.

252
00:15:41,048 --> 00:15:42,518
Getting more and more skilled.

253
00:15:47,329 --> 00:15:48,487
It's still a bit...

254
00:15:50,840 --> 00:15:53,764
It's okay, this cup is for you.

255
00:15:53,844 --> 00:15:57,528
This tulip is so life like and vivid.

256
00:15:58,421 --> 00:16:00,447
I cannot bear to drink it.

257
00:16:00,930 --> 00:16:03,612
