260
00:16:11,036 --> 00:16:14,435
Are the younger generation these days,
all so hypocritical?

261
00:16:15,297 --> 00:16:16,972
Everything I say is the honest truth,
okay?

262
00:16:17,052 --> 00:16:19,336
That's right.
Do not slander our friendship.

263
00:16:19,416 --> 00:16:21,508
Go, mind your own business,
don't bother us.

264
00:16:21,588 --> 00:16:23,079
