Let's have a taste.

266
00:16:25,461 --> 00:16:26,575
Taste it, taste it.

267
00:16:30,552 --> 00:16:31,605
How is it?

268
00:16:36,386 --> 00:16:37,310
It's okay.

269
00:16:37,390 --> 00:16:38,471
Not bad.

270
00:16:39,134 --> 00:16:41,435
Sure enough, hard work pays off.

271
00:16:42,845 --> 00:16:45,589
I am feeling more confident
about your coffee competition now.

272
00:16:45,669 --> 00:16:46,828
Try your best.

273
00:16:46,908 --> 00:16:48,043
Okay.

274
00:16:49,057 --> 00:16:50,021
What's wrong?

275
00:16:50,399 --> 00:16:51,803
What else is unsatisfactory?

276
00:16:54,076 --> 00:16:56,559
I have confidence
when it comes to the taste of coffee.

277
00:16:56,639 --> 00:16:58,706
-Okay.
-But this pattern...

278
00:16:59,320 --> 00:17:03,128
Although baristas
think latte art is optional,

279
00:17:03,208 --> 00:17:05,865
but I myself quite enjoy doing latte art.

280
00:17:05,945 --> 00:17:08,099
And I think it's also quite important.

281
00:17:08,179 --> 00:17:09,061
That's right.

282
00:17:09,141 --> 00:17:12,357
Of course, what you like
is the most important, it's okay.

283
00:17:12,862 --> 00:17:16,630
Although there are improvements
in my skills everyday.

284
00:17:17,017 --> 00:17:19,818
But these patterns,
I just keep imitating them.

285
00:17:19,898 --> 00:17:21,679
But no breakthrough at all.

286
00:17:22,544 --> 00:17:25,820
The highest level of latte art
is originality.

287
00:17:30,371 --> 00:17:31,598
Boss Yi is right.

288
00:17:31,678 --> 00:17:33,000
I have to be original.

289
00:17:44,054 --> 00:17:45,416
How will you hold a pen?

290
00:17:47,594 --> 00:17:49,907
I think I can do it again,
isn't it just an exam?

291
00:17:49,987 --> 00:17:51,352
Can't trouble me, Xia Rui.

292
00:17:52,076 --> 00:17:53,243
Have a taste.

293
00:17:59,192 --> 00:18:00,245
Is it nice?

294
00:18:01,931 --> 00:18:02,946
Yes.

295
00:18:03,499 --> 00:18:06,208
This is a new product
developed by our boss today.

296
00:18:06,289 --> 00:18:08,767
Besides having a hint of fragrance...

297
00:18:15,796 --> 00:18:17,684
There are 10,000 viewers?

298
00:18:24,348 --> 00:18:26,085
Your fingerprint is more than enough.

299
00:18:26,507 --> 00:18:28,217
Got it, hurry up.

300
00:18:28,297 --> 00:18:29,404
We're late.

301
00:18:43,576 --> 00:18:44,829
Sorry, sorry.

302
00:18:44,909 --> 00:18:46,040
Hi, everyone.

303
00:18:46,120 --> 00:18:48,226
Anyway, I'm teaching you
how to make coffee today.

304
00:18:48,306 --> 00:18:50,417
I will show the demonstration directly.

305
00:18:50,497 --> 00:18:52,924
Don't turn it off.
No, surely the operation is wrong.

306
00:18:53,004 --> 00:18:55,041
I'll do it again. I'll do it another way.

307
00:19:04,357 --> 00:19:06,218
It's fine, exams are more important.

308
00:19:06,298 --> 00:19:08,654
I'm only gone for one day.
I'll be back soon.

309
00:19:20,574 --> 00:19:23,072
Don't rush, take it slow.

310
00:19:24,512 --> 00:19:25,858
Look, like this.

311
00:20:08,792 --> 00:20:10,720
Goodnight, Xia Rui.

312
00:20:24,091 --> 00:20:25,048
Nan Xi.

313
00:20:28,363 --> 00:20:29,665
Do your best in the exam.

314
00:20:30,466 --> 00:20:31,438
Okay.

315
00:20:38,518 --> 00:20:40,791
Your competition, try your best.

316
00:20:41,290 --> 00:20:42,300
Okay.

317
00:20:42,724 --> 00:20:45,885
I hereby announce,
the World Barista competition.

318
00:20:45,965 --> 00:20:49,462
Eastern China preliminary rounds
officially begin.

319
00:21:51,436 --> 00:21:54,388
Next, we'll invite the judges
to come on stage to score.

320
00:22:09,579 --> 00:22:12,159
There are two components
that are making your coffee.

321
00:22:12,239 --> 00:22:13,466
What's the...

322
00:22:13,546 --> 00:22:15,537
The first is syrup.

323
00:22:15,617 --> 00:22:17,046
What is the second one?

324
00:22:18,518 --> 00:22:19,667
Pu Er Tea.

325
00:22:20,422 --> 00:22:21,704
Extraordinary.

326
00:22:24,924 --> 00:22:25,975
Interesting.

327
00:22:56,311 --> 00:22:59,355
I hereby announce five contestants
entering the finals.

328
00:22:59,435 --> 00:23:05,745
They are Fang Huaien, Xia Rui, Wu Tingyou,
Lin Zhiyao and Zhuoling.

329
00:23:09,412 --> 00:23:10,438
As expected.

330
00:23:14,913 --> 00:23:16,602
Congratulations to these contestants.

331
00:23:28,833 --> 00:23:33,840
2017 World Barista Competition
Eastern China Region Rematch...

332
00:23:33,920 --> 00:23:36,364
will officially start in three hours.

333
00:23:36,444 --> 00:23:38,292
To all the contestants, do your best.

334
00:23:54,254 --> 00:23:56,755
Students, get ready for the exam.

335
00:23:56,835 --> 00:23:59,586
Please put away your phones.

336
00:23:59,666 --> 00:24:02,008
This exam is very important.

337
00:24:02,088 --> 00:24:04,976
I hope everyone will take it seriously.

338
00:24:10,272 --> 00:24:12,361
Boss Yi, I'll go to the bathroom.

339
00:24:31,583 --> 00:24:33,738
Xia Rui, what's wrong?

340
00:24:33,818 --> 00:24:36,528
Boss Yi, I did not prepare anything
for the rematch.

341
00:24:36,608 --> 00:24:38,578
What should I do next?

342
00:24:38,658 --> 00:24:39,988
Are you nervous?

343
00:24:40,068 --> 00:24:41,546
How can I not be?

344
00:24:41,626 --> 00:24:43,182
Please don't scare me.

345
00:24:43,262 --> 00:24:46,179
How is it possible that
Xia Rui is nervous.

346
00:24:46,259 --> 00:24:49,839
Stop teasing me already, please help me.

347
00:24:49,919 --> 00:24:51,707
-I'm nervous.
-Okay, okay.

348
00:24:52,254 --> 00:24:54,332
Do you remember what I told you before?

349
00:24:55,208 --> 00:24:56,966
Empty your mind.

350
00:24:57,046 --> 00:24:59,043
And only think about
the person you love most.

351
00:24:59,123 --> 00:25:01,893
Coffee made in this way, is the best.

352
00:25:05,237 --> 00:25:07,575
The person I love most.

353
00:25:09,677 --> 00:25:12,134
Thirty minutes have passed.

354
00:25:12,214 --> 00:25:14,020
Please answer the paper carefully.

355
00:25:14,840 --> 00:25:16,214
Read carefully.

356
00:25:20,267 --> 00:25:21,471
Nan Xi.

357
00:25:21,958 --> 00:25:23,480
Professor, I have something urgent.

358
00:25:23,560 --> 00:25:24,812
This, you...

359
00:25:43,957 --> 00:25:46,980
Baby whale? You made this?

360
00:25:48,293 --> 00:25:51,635
I will call you Woodie from now on.

361
00:25:51,715 --> 00:25:53,180
You can call me little bell.

362
00:25:53,260 --> 00:25:56,408
Baby whale is our secret.

363
00:25:56,488 --> 00:25:58,363
You can't tell anyone else.

364
00:26:00,434 --> 00:26:05,111
Nan Xi, I think I am pretty timid.

365
00:26:05,765 --> 00:26:08,850
Especially scared of losing things.

366
00:26:10,582 --> 00:26:13,425
Just like you, lost and recovered.

367
00:26:15,426 --> 00:26:18,331
I'll be here, don't be afraid.

368
00:26:20,694 --> 00:26:22,066
I've told you.

369
00:26:22,866 --> 00:26:24,114
You are my end.

370
00:26:47,687 --> 00:26:48,790
Xia Rui.

371
00:26:49,542 --> 00:26:53,262
Promise me, always be my end.

372
00:27:04,990 --> 00:27:07,573
I can't believe
you learned how to do latte art.

373
00:27:08,472 --> 00:27:09,942
Did you learn from Boss Yi?

374
00:27:11,097 --> 00:27:12,128
Guess.

375
00:27:12,767 --> 00:27:14,050
When you got into Binhai University,

376
00:27:14,130 --> 00:27:16,571
it was you
who gave me courage and confidence.

377
00:27:17,029 --> 00:27:20,581
This latte art is one of my memories.

378
00:27:30,473 --> 00:27:33,459
One cannot be too delicate with latte art.

379
00:27:33,539 --> 00:27:36,423
Which is why the pattern
cannot be too complicated.

380
00:27:37,433 --> 00:27:38,759
If you emphasize on the beauty.

381
00:27:39,093 --> 00:27:41,053
You can add some decoration on it.

382
00:27:55,729 --> 00:27:57,314
What's the matter?

383
00:27:57,765 --> 00:27:58,863
You're so cute.

384
00:29:12,569 --> 00:29:14,566
Okay, all the coffees are completed.

385
00:29:14,646 --> 00:29:17,425
We'll invite the judges
to come on stage to score.

386
00:29:19,449 --> 00:29:22,094
The annual World Barista Competition...

387
00:29:22,174 --> 00:29:25,572
East China Region rematch
is coming to an end.

388
00:29:25,652 --> 00:29:31,635
Which barista from our East China Region
can make it to the finals?

389
00:29:32,313 --> 00:29:36,507
I hereby announce, the top three finalists
making it to the finals.

390
00:29:36,910 --> 00:29:39,426
They are Wu Tingyou.

391
00:29:44,247 --> 00:29:45,719
Lin Zhiyao.

392
00:29:49,215 --> 00:29:53,520
And the champion for this
East China Region Preliminary Round is...

393
00:29:54,002 --> 00:29:55,434
Zhuoling, congratulations!

394
00:30:00,772 --> 00:30:02,079
Congratulations to all the winners.

395
00:30:02,159 --> 00:30:05,984
Let's welcome Mr. Umberto
to hand out the awards for the winners.

396
00:30:11,530 --> 00:30:12,694
Nan Xi.

397
00:30:13,858 --> 00:30:14,929
Nan Xi.

398
00:30:15,940 --> 00:30:17,279
Nan Xi.

399
00:30:18,297 --> 00:30:22,453
It was already unexpected for me
to enter the rematch, right?

400
00:30:24,807 --> 00:30:25,776
Yes.

401
00:30:26,808 --> 00:30:28,598
Didn't you have an exam today?

402
00:30:30,039 --> 00:30:30,983
Yes.

403
00:30:31,407 --> 00:30:32,956
You finished the paper?

404
00:30:36,960 --> 00:30:37,941
Yes.

405
00:30:38,342 --> 00:30:40,079
Our Woodie is a genius indeed.

406
00:30:41,591 --> 00:30:42,777
Thank you.

407
00:30:43,931 --> 00:30:46,573
The coffee I made today, was my best.

408
00:30:46,653 --> 00:30:48,060
Do you want to have a taste?

409
00:30:50,527 --> 00:30:51,469
Yes.

410
00:30:51,549 --> 00:30:53,593
I'll make it for you
when we go back to Binhai.

411
00:30:55,375 --> 00:30:56,359
Okay.

412
00:31:04,959 --> 00:31:05,963
Xia Rui.

413
00:31:06,043 --> 00:31:06,952
Mr. Umberto.

414
00:31:07,032 --> 00:31:09,401
Although you didn't win anything
this competition,

415
00:31:09,481 --> 00:31:11,953
my biggest surprise this time
was discovering you.

416
00:31:12,637 --> 00:31:13,625
Me?

417
00:31:14,298 --> 00:31:17,488
Your sense of taste
and understanding of coffee.

418
00:31:17,569 --> 00:31:20,987
I haven't seen a barista
like this in years.

419
00:31:22,865 --> 00:31:23,832
Thank you, sir.

420
00:31:23,912 --> 00:31:25,879
I really like making coffee.

421
00:31:26,650 --> 00:31:27,838
I've seen your information.

422
00:31:27,918 --> 00:31:30,485
You are now a university student
majoring in management.

423
00:31:30,565 --> 00:31:31,660
Correct.

424
00:31:31,740 --> 00:31:34,407
Have you thought about coming to Italy?

425
00:31:34,487 --> 00:31:39,045
To learn how to be a professional barista.

426
00:31:41,187 --> 00:31:43,712
Me? Italy?

427
00:31:43,792 --> 00:31:45,473
I'll give you my business card.

428
00:31:47,537 --> 00:31:49,228
To be exact, it's with me.

429
00:31:49,308 --> 00:31:51,759
As long as you pass our language test,

430
00:31:51,839 --> 00:31:54,078
I'm willing to be your referrer.

431
00:31:54,168 --> 00:31:58,435
And undergo a one year barista training
in our school.

432
00:32:06,840 --> 00:32:08,152
Thank you, Mr. Umberto.

433
00:32:08,232 --> 00:32:10,894
I am grateful for your recognition.

434
00:32:10,974 --> 00:32:13,963
But I am sorry that
I am unable to accept your invitation.

435
00:32:14,043 --> 00:32:17,355
Do you mind if I ask why?

436
00:32:17,435 --> 00:32:21,443
Because when I graduated high school,
my mother wanted me to go abroad.

437
00:32:21,523 --> 00:32:23,488
In order to stay in China back then,

438
00:32:23,568 --> 00:32:26,163
we put in a lot of effort
and tried our best.

439
00:32:26,243 --> 00:32:30,112
If I go abroad this time,
all our efforts back then will be wasted.

440
00:32:31,367 --> 00:32:33,511
-You guys?
-Yes, us.

441
00:32:33,591 --> 00:32:37,046
Without us, I would be unable
to draw the baby whale pattern.

442
00:32:37,126 --> 00:32:38,223
I understand.

443
00:32:38,303 --> 00:32:41,715
People who are more important than dreams,
should be treasured.

444
00:32:41,795 --> 00:32:45,439
I respect your choice,
if you ever change your mind,

445
00:32:45,859 --> 00:32:48,099
please feel free to contact me.

446
00:32:48,179 --> 00:32:49,517
Thank you, Mr. Umberto.

447
00:32:50,309 --> 00:32:51,478
Thank you.

448
00:32:54,353 --> 00:32:57,994
It seems that Mr. Umberto
really appreciates you.

449
00:32:59,606 --> 00:33:00,648
Xia Rui.

450
00:33:03,525 --> 00:33:04,419
Let me.

451
00:33:04,499 --> 00:33:06,208
Why have you been in the bathroom
for so long?

452
00:33:06,288 --> 00:33:08,679
I really want to go,
please wait for me, okay?
